import { Element } from "react-scroll";
import { Container } from "react-bootstrap";
import { Title, Text, Section } from "../core";

import WorkIcon from "../../assets/icons/Discord";
import PlayIcon from "../../assets/icons/Play";
import BlubIcon from "../../assets/icons/LightBlub";

import { VerticalTimeline, VerticalTimelineElement }  from 'react-vertical-timeline-component';

function Roadmap() {

return (
<>
<Element name="roadmap" id="roadmap">
    <Section className="pt-4 pb-0">
      <Container>
                <Title variant="secSm" className="my-5 pb-lg-4">
                    Roadmap
                </Title>
            <VerticalTimeline>
              <VerticalTimelineElement
                className="vertical-timeline-element--phase1"
                contentArrowStyle={{ borderRight: '7px solid  #fff' }}
                date="2022 May"
                iconStyle={{ background: 'rgb(16, 204, 82)', color: '#fff' }}
                icon={<PlayIcon />}
              >
                 <Title variant="cardBig" className="mb-4">
                  01. Phase
                </Title>
                <Text variant="p" >In phase one, Pixie Bears wake up and share the story of their plans. Taking the Website
                  and Discord out of the den, and putting the worthy membears on the list.</Text>
              </VerticalTimelineElement>
              <VerticalTimelineElement
                className="vertical-timeline-element--phase2"
                date="2022 Jun"
              
                icon={<WorkIcon />}
              >
                <Title variant="cardBig" className="mb-4">
                  02. Phase
                </Title>
                <Text variant="p" >After Phase one, it is the time to start giving out rewards in Phase two. Creative-hearted membears will be rewarded handsomely. For all membears there are many
                    Giveaways. Collabs!</Text>
              </VerticalTimelineElement>
              <VerticalTimelineElement
                className="vertical-timeline-element--phase3"
                date="2022 - July"
             
                icon={<BlubIcon />}
              >
                <Title variant="cardBig" className="mb-4">
                  03. Phase
                </Title>
                <Text variant="p" >All the Phase one and two work makes Phase 3 that much more beneficial for all the
                    membears. WL Mint, Live Mint, Sold Out, Secondary Market Listing, all in Phase 3.</Text>
              </VerticalTimelineElement>
              <VerticalTimelineElement
                className="vertical-timeline-element--phase4"
                date="2022 Avg"
              
                icon={<WorkIcon />}
              >
                <Title variant="cardBig" className="mb-4">
                  04. Phase
                </Title>
                <Text variant="p" >Phase four is where OGs are will enjoy the $20000 giveaway, everybody is able to
                    stake their NFT`s and tokens. Pixieverse development is on the way, and with it
                    Roadmap 2.0. Slick Merch</Text>
              </VerticalTimelineElement>
             
              <VerticalTimelineElement
                iconStyle={{ background: 'rgb(16, 204, 82)', color: '#fff' }}
                icon={<WorkIcon />}
              />
            </VerticalTimeline>
      </Container>
  </Section>
</Element>


</>
);


}


export default Roadmap;
